| Data Point | Visual Type | Action Title |
|------------|-------------|--------------|
| | | |

**Visual Type ‚Üí Chart Type Mapping** (for Stage 4 handoff):
| Visual Type (P3) | Recommended Chart Types (P4) | Best When |
|------------------|------------------------------|-----------|
| Data visualization | `bar_vertical`, `bar_horizontal` | Comparing discrete categories |
| Trend/Change | `line`, `area` | Showing change over time |
| Comparison | `bar_horizontal`, `table` | Ranking or side-by-side comparison |
| Proportion/Share | `pie`, `donut`, `stacked_bar` | Part-to-whole relationships |
| Timeline | `timeline`, `gantt` | Sequential events with dates |
| Relationship | `scatter`, `bubble` | Correlation between variables |
| Process/Flow | `diagram`, `flowchart` | Steps or decision trees |
| Geographic | `map`, `choropleth` | Location-based data |

